column2: SELECT     m.objid as gal_id, m.ra AS gal_ra, m.dec AS gal_dec,     n.objid as star_id, n.distance,     o.ra AS star_ra, o.dec AS star_dec     into mydb.micadomatches from MyDB.micadogals AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    JOIN mydb.micadostars AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
